## Maintenance

| Task | Frequency | Notes |
|------|-----------|-------|
| Clear `plans/` | Monthly | Old session plans, safe to delete |
| Clear `history.jsonl` | As needed | Can grow to several MB |
| Clear `debug/` | As needed | Debug logs |
| Review CLAUDE.md | Quarterly | Update conventions as needed |

